      ],
      "explanation": "$d/3 - d/4 = 1/2 \\Rightarrow d/12 = 1/2 \\Rightarrow d = 6$ km.",
      "steps": [
        {
          "text": "**Let distance = $d$ km.** Time at 3 km/h: $d/3$ h. Time at 4 km/h: $d/4$ h."
        },
        {
          "text": "**The 4 km/h trip saves 30 min** ($= 1/2$ h):"
        },
        {
          "math": "\\dfrac{d}{3} - \\dfrac{d}{4} = \\dfrac{1}{2}"
        },
        {
          "math": "\\dfrac{4d - 3d}{12} = \\dfrac{1}{2}"
        },
        {
          "math": "\\dfrac{d}{12} = \\dfrac{1}{2} \\;\\Longrightarrow\\; d = 6 \\text{ km}"
        }
      ],
      "difficulty": "hard"
